metadata.name: Freedom
metadata.description:
The burden of society, the chains of expectations, and the struggles of life. They hold you back and constrict you. Yet, what you see in the distance is not an illusion. Make your own choices, and escape from your prison. Life is beautiful. 

Resolution: 9216x6144 PNG
Made with: Midjourney, Disco Diffusion, & Krita
Resized with: Gigapixel
